---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="The crew’s log"
  description="A calm maritime archive of Cyprus — botanical, geological, historical, religious, and linguistic observations collected with care."
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pt-11 pb-14">
    <div class="max-w-[62ch]">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs tracking-[2px] text-[#5f5f5f] mb-2">
        <span>CYPRUS</span>
        <span class="inline-block w-6 h-px bg-[#5f5f5f]/40"></span>
        <span>AT SEA</span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="font-serif text-[50px] leading-[1.0] tracking-[-1.7px] text-[#1c1c1c]">
        The crew’s log
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-4 text-[16.5px] leading-relaxed text-[#3c3c3c]">
        A quiet collection of observations from the shores, mountains, and waters of Cyprus.
        What the island reveals — in leaf and stone, in old words, and in memory.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Calm, prominent category currents — no pills, no cards -->
    <div class="mt-10 max-w-[62ch]">
      <div class="text-[10px] tracking-[1.5px] text-[#6a6a6a] mb-3">THE CURRENTS</div>

      <div class="space-y-5 text-[15px]">
        <a href="/archive?topic=Botany" class="group flex items-baseline gap-3 hover:text-black transition-colors">
          <span class="block h-px w-7 shrink-0 bg-[#166534] group-hover:w-9 transition-all self-center"></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-x-[0.5em]">
            <span class="font-medium text-[#166534]">Botany</span>
            <span class="inline-block w-[0.8em] h-px bg-[#8a8a8a] align-middle"></span>
            <span class="text-[#4a4a4a] group-hover:text-[#333]">trees, groves, resin, and the green life of the island</span>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/archive?topic=Geology" class="group flex items-baseline gap-3 hover:text-black transition-colors">
          <span class="block h-px w-7 shrink-0 bg-[#92400e] group-hover:w-9 transition-all self-center"></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-x-[0.5em]">
            <span class="font-medium text-[#92400e]">Geology</span>
            <span class="inline-block w-[0.8em] h-px bg-[#8a8a8a] align-middle"></span>
            <span class="text-[#4a4a4a] group-hover:text-[#333]">the ancient stone and the sea floor lifted into mountains</span>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/archive?topic=History" class="group flex items-baseline gap-3 hover:text-black transition-colors">
          <span class="block h-px w-7 shrink-0 bg-[#1e3a5f] group-hover:w-9 transition-all self-center"></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-x-[0.5em]">
            <span class="font-medium text-[#1e3a5f]">History</span>
            <span class="inline-block w-[0.8em] h-px bg-[#8a8a8a] align-middle"></span>
            <span class="text-[#4a4a4a] group-hover:text-[#333]">fragments of time, commanderies, and those who crossed these waters</span>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/archive?topic=Religion" class="group flex items-baseline gap-3 hover:text-black transition-colors">
          <span class="block h-px w-7 shrink-0 bg-[#854d0e] group-hover:w-9 transition-all self-center"></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-x-[0.5em]">
            <span class="font-medium text-[#854d0e]">Religion</span>
            <span class="inline-block w-[0.8em] h-px bg-[#8a8a8a] align-middle"></span>
            <span class="text-[#4a4a4a] group-hover:text-[#333]">painted churches, quiet devotions, and the long thread of the sacred</span>
          </span>
        </a>

        <a href="/archive?topic=Language" class="group flex items-baseline gap-3 hover:text-black transition-colors">
          <span class="block h-px w-7 shrink-0 bg-[#1e40af] group-hover:w-9 transition-all self-center"></span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-x-[0.5em]">
            <span class="font-medium text-[#1e40af]">Language</span>
            <span class="inline-block w-[0.8em] h-px bg-[#8a8a8a] align-middle"></span>
            <span class="text-[#4a4a4a] group-hover:text-[#333]">words, names, and the memory carried in Greek and older tongues</span>
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-9 max-w-[62ch]">
      <div class="wave-divider"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 text-xs text-[#666] max-w-[55ch]">
      A living logbook. New entries appear as the crew returns from the field.
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
